title: Embrace (Evolve #2)by S.E. Hall
description:
Evan Allen is a handsome, athletic, southern
gentleman who now attends Georgia Southern
University for no good reason.

After what he expected to be the romantic gesture
of the century, Evan is looking at no friends, a year
of ineligibility on the football team, and no girl.

He's starting over alone and doesn't know quite how to
proceed. Certain members of The Crew refuse to let him f
ace things by himself, taking him under their wing, and it
doesn't take the ladies long to notice him, either.

Sometimes life doesn't go as you had planned.
Sometimes it goes better.

Embrace it.



Embrace (Evolve #2)
by S.E. Hall
